  "response": "In the Twain Harte, California area, several reputable solar panel installation providers can help with solar energy projects. Here are a few you might consider:\n\n1. **SolarCity (Tesla Energy)** - They have a significant presence in California and offer a range of solar products and services.\n\n2. **SunPower** - Known for high-efficiency solar panels and comprehensive installation services.\n\n3. **Sierra Solar Systems** - A local option that provides installations in the Sierra Nevada region and nearby areas.\n\n4. **Barkley Solar Electric** - A local provider that might offer personalized service and expertise in the Twain Harte area.\n\n5. **Skyline Solar** - Offers custom solar solutions and has several locations in California.\n\nIt's a good idea to research each company, check their reviews, and possibly get quotes from multiple installers to compare pricing and services. Local community forums or review sites like Yelp and Google Reviews might provide additional insights and customer experiences.",
